s method is called when the user taps on the body of the callout view, as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"opposed to the callout’s left or right accessory view. If the annotation has a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom callout view via the "},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method, this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is only called whenever the callout view calls its delegate’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutViewDelegate\/calloutViewTapped:","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If this method is present on the delegate, the standard callout view’s body"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"momentarily highlights when the user taps it, whether or not this method does"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"anything in response to the tap."}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Display custom views as callouts, learn how to trigger an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"action when an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"s ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is tapped.","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"title":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L1006","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","title":"MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutViewDelegate/calloutViewTapped:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the callout view has been tapped."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutviewdelegate\/calloutviewtapped:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"calloutViewTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"calloutViewTapped:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutViewDelegate\/calloutViewTapped:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"calloutViewTapped:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:taponcalloutforannotation:","title":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped on an annotation’s callout view."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapViewDelegate"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate"}}}